article.description: — Isaiah Stevens had 19 points and David Roddy posted 19 points and eight rebounds as Colorado State rolled past Air Force 72-49 on Saturday.
article.headline: Colorado St. beats Air Force 72-49
article.story: FORT COLLINS, Colo. -- — Isaiah Stevens had 19 points and David Roddy posted 19 points and eight rebounds as Colorado State rolled past Air Force 72-49 on Saturday. Stevens made 5 of 6 3-pointers. Adam Thistlewood had 14 points for Colorado State (15-4, 12-3 Mountain West Conference). John Tonje added 11 points. A.J. Walker had 13 points for the Falcons (5-18, 3-16). Carter Murphy added 10 points.
